{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"98837cf487","title":"陈伯达关于贯彻执行毛主席最新最高指示的指示","origin":"周良霄、顾菊英编《疯狂、扭曲与堕落的年代》之二——《十年文革中首长讲话传信录》, 2009。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"da8c8bbb12","index":0,"year":1967,"month":12,"day":7,"articleId":"98837cf487"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"aa9434abe4","name":"北京文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"e46e45351b","name":"陈伯达","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"48606ca4e5","name":"陈伯达"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"55f16911a6","type":"title","text":"陈伯达关于贯彻执行毛主席最新最高指示的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"98837cf487"},{"id":"6bfda03ba8","type":"authors","text":"陈伯达","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"98837cf487"},{"id":"76fc77f8d3","type":"paragraph","text":"十二月七日北京卫戍区直属办公室主任哈斯在北京工学院传达了陈伯达同志关于贯彻执行毛主席最新最高指示的指示：","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"98837cf487"},{"id":"ed923a63ac","type":"paragraph","text":"一、毛主席的指示要认真执行，不准曲解，要不折不扣执行，在执行过程要坚决反对两面派的态度。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"98837cf487"},{"id":"47ca3ee65b","type":"paragraph","text":"二、要普遍的办起训练班，要斗私批修，学习最新指示、老三篇，林副主席“八·九”讲话。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"98837cf487"},{"id":"e531e9c7c5","type":"paragraph","text":"三、要向先进单位学习，向工人阶级学习。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"98837cf487"}],"page":{"id":"e56c971979","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"98837cf487","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}